BVaccination toFPROTECT YOUR BABY

BWhy bother?
FTo protect against four diseases that
Fare potential killers:

CDIPHTHERIAGan infectious disease of the throat. Very catching.

CTETANUSGalso called lockjaw because it  causes very painful muscle spasms.
 Caught from dirty cuts and wounds.

CWHOOPING COUGH-Ghighly infectious and
Gdangerous to young children.
GMay permanently damage their lungs.

CPOLIOGhighly infectious virus which may;Gcause permanent paralysis or death.

FHow to protect your baby: Key _
